.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, chess, canasta
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, dancer, doctor, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, mouse
 1. the person playing chess is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person playing snooker is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the accountant is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the writer##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | snooker  | canasta | chess     | mah-jongg |
| Job           | doctor  | writer      | accountant | dancer    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Pet           | horse   | mouse       | fish       | frog      |

